snippet.title: Amber Heard Shows Photos Of Johnny Depp’s Alleged Lunch, Cocaine And Whiskey
snippet.description: Actress Amber  showed a photo in court Wednesday of Johnny ’s alleged lunch.  The “lunch” included a pint of whiskey, four lines of cocaine and a pill box, according to a report published by the . The photo was reportedly taken at 1:38 p.m. in 2013. Another photo of  passed out on the floor was also shown to the court.     The photos were taken by  before the couple had a fight over ’s drug use. The “lunch” was had by  while he was reportedly supposed to be filming a documentary on Keith Richards of The Rolling Stones.  When asked if  was carrying cocaine in the pillbox he responded, “I would say I probably was.”   The photos are just part of an intense court battle between  and The Sun.  is suing the outlet for publishing an article calling him a “wife-beater.”     claimed in court that  gave hime the whiskey. “Well she poured me the whisky and cocaine was visible in front of her, and I have experienced many times with Ms.  that she would in fact chop the cocaine up for me so that I could do the line and then she would press her finger into it and ingest it orally,” he reportedly said in court. “I’m not suggesting that she did that in this case, but I am suggesting that it was a normal duty that she felt obligated to do,” he added.
